                     <p>West-Haddon.

   <persName nymRef="Godelef">
                           <forename>Emma</forename> daughter of <persName>
                              <forename>William</forename> 
                              <surname>Godelef</surname> of <placeName role="person" key="place_108032">West Haddon</placeName>
                           </persName>
                        </persName> claims to <persName>
                           <forename>Geoffrey</forename> son of  <persName>
                              <forename>John</forename> of <surname>Stowe</surname>
                           </persName>
                        </persName>, her right in a messuage with a garden and croft which fell to her of the inheritance of <persName nymRef="Godelef">her brother <forename>William</forename>
                        </persName> in <placeName key="place_108032">W<supplied>est</supplied> H<supplied>addon</supplied>
                        </placeName>. 
   Witnesses: <persName>
                           <forename>John</forename> 
                           <surname>Herbert</surname> of <placeName role="person" key="place_108032">W<supplied>est</supplied> H<supplied>addon</supplied>
                           </placeName>
                        </persName>, 
   <persName>
                           <forename>Richard</forename> 
                           <surname type="patronymic">son of Robert</surname>
                        </persName>, 
   <persName>
                           <forename>William</forename> de <surname>Cotes</surname>
                        </persName>, 
   <persName>
                           <forename>John</forename> le <surname>freman</surname>
                        </persName>, 
   <persName>
                           <forename>John</forename> de <surname>Stowe</surname>
                        </persName> of the same. 
   Given at <placeName role="date" key="place_108032">W<supplied>est</supplied> H<supplied>addon</supplied>
                        </placeName> 
                        <origDate when="1322-04-08">
                           <supplied>8 April 1322.</supplied>
                        </origDate>
                     </p>
